(1, 'Sugacci GLAMOUR - Perfume for Men and Women - 50ml', 'Sugacci GLAMOUR - Perfume for Men and Women - 50ml', 'Sugacci, GLAMOUR ,Perfume for Men and Women ,50ml', 'A perfect mix of spices, leather and chocolate lets you have a glamorous day amongst your peers leaving your fragrance trail all day long! Sugacci GLAMOUR is a bold and elegant Perfume for Men and Women packed in Eau de Parfum concentration, Unisex, long lasting, preferred by people who are confident and bold as a personality.', 'A perfect mix of spices, leather and chocolate lets you have a glamorous day amongst your peers leaving your fragrance trail all day long! Sugacci GLAMOUR ', '500', '449', 'en', 'Sugacci_GLAMOUR_-_Perfume_for_Men_and_Women_-_50ml1.jpg', 1661447494, 2, 'male', 4, 10, 1, 'Sugacci_GLAMOUR_-_Perfume_for_Men_and_Women_-_50ml'),
(2, 'Sugacci LA PAZZO - Perfume for Men and Women - 50ml', 'Sugacci LA PAZZO - Perfume for Men and Women - 50ml', 'Sugacci ,LA, PAZZO, Perfume for Men and Women ,50ml', 'Sugacci LA  PAZZO, a party-wear Unisex fragrance; made in Eau de Parfum concentration for the crazy; for the wild party-animals out there. A rich blend of citrus fruits and flowers, uniquely blended with leather and wood to help you party harder all-night and make your presence felt in the room. A specific party-wear perfume for men and women who want to smell nice throughout the night!', 'Sugacci LA  PAZZO, a party-wear Unisex fragrance; made in Eau de Parfum concentration for the crazy; for the wild party-animals out there. ', '300', '249', 'en', 'Sugacci_LA_PAZZO_-_Perfume_for_Men_and_Women_-_50ml.jpg', 1661448169, 1, 'male', 4, 10, 1, 'Sugacci_LA_PAZZO_-_Perfume_for_Men_and_Women_-_50ml'),
(3, 'Sugacci VIBRANTE - Perfume for Men and Women - 50ml', 'Sugacci VIBRANTE - Perfume for Men and Women - 50ml', 'Sugacci,VIBRANTE, Perfume for Men and Women ,50ml', 'The Sugacci Vibrante Eau de Parfum is an immensely fresh fruity Perfume for Men and Women with woody base notes making it the best unisex fragrance. This 50ml perfume is a strong and a long lasting smell which is made from the finest hand-picked extracts of melons, cocoa and accords, blended with vanilla marshmallows and cedar wood to give you an enchanting and lasting all-time-wear fragrance. Vibrante will keep you fresh all day long and is ideal for daywear & office-wear!', 'The Sugacci Vibrante Eau de Parfum is an immensely fresh fruity Perfume for Men and Women with woody base notes making it the best unisex fragrance. ', '300', '255', 'en', 'Sugacci_VIBRANTE_-_Perfume_for_Men_and_Women_-_50ml.jpg', 1661448221, 1, 'both', 3, 10, 3, 'Sugacci_VIBRANTE_-_Perfume_for_Men_and_Women_-_50ml');
